items.headline: Welcome to Age of Empires Online, a MMO RTS game.
items.desc: Age of Empires Online Wiki is dedicated to Age of Empires Online (often abbreviated to AoEO), a free-to-play history-based real-time strategy video game released on August 16th, 2011. Age of Empires Online is a Free-to-Play game with Premium Content, it has been dubbed a "Freemium" game. Almost all of the games content may be enjoyed as a Free player. In this Wiki, you may find out great information about the game. If it's quests, units, or even just for fun.
